'''Arrif''' neɣ '''Arif''' d tamnaḍt [[Azrar n idurar|tamsedrart]] tezga-d di ugafa n [[Lmerruk]], tessajja ɣef [[Ilel Agrakal|Yilel agrakal]], zeddɣen deg-s 4 imelyan n yimezdaɣ yessawalen Tamaziɣt.

Seg yiɣerman imeqqṛanen i yellan di temnaḍt n Arrif Ameqqran ɣer-neɣ: [[Nnaḍur]], [[Lḥusima]], [[Miḍar]], [[Targist]], [[Azɣenɣan]], [[Seřwan]], [[Zayyu]], [[Berkan]], [[Aɛarwi]], [[Driwec]], [[At Buɛeyyac]], [[Kassita|Qasita]], [[Imzuren]] d [[Ajdir]]. 

Idurar n Arif udsen ar idurar n ''Ordillera Bética'' n wenẓul n [[Spenya]]. Akken daɣen i yudsen ɣer Yidurar n Waṭlas maca wer qqinen ɣur-sen wer llin d-amur deg-sen. Gar-asen tella [[Taza (Merruk)|Taza]].

Iwdan yessawalen [[Tamaziɣt Tarifant]] di Arif qqaren i yiman-nsen “[[Imaziɣen]]” neɣ “Irifiyen”, maca tutlayt nsen qqaṛen as “Tamaziɣt” mačči "Tarifit". Iwdan n berra i Arif d nitni i d-as-yeqqaren Tarifit.

